              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6010851495265360471">I reread the seires through audible. What a delight. I totally forgot I enjoyed them all those years ago. Now that I actually went to San Francisco in 2010, the descriptions made much better sense, too. It was a fun and nostalgic read.</span>

          </span>
